Class TLoopStmt

  • java.lang.Object
    • gudusoft.gsqlparser.nodes.TParseTreeNode

          • gudusoft.gsqlparser.stmt.TLoopStmt
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitable

    public class TLoopStmt
extends TBlockSqlStatement
    A LOOP statement executes a sequence of statements multiple times. PL/SQL provides these loop statements:
    • Basic loop
    • WHILE loop
    • FOR loop

      FOR indexName IN lower_bound .. upper_bound LOOP statements END LOOP

    • Cursor FOR loop
    See Also:
